headline: Colgate-Palmolive (CL) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Colgate-Palmolive (CL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +4.02% and +2.79%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Can Clorox Deliver a Q2 Earnings Beat Despite Cost Headwinds?
summary: CLX's Q2 results may reflect revenue and EPS declines as inflation-driven cost pressures and ERP disruptions weigh on margins despite brand strength.
